'''Nigeria''' is an original [[Nations|country]] that was on BitLife in September 2018. Its default city is only the largest Nigerian city, Lagos. Strangely, it's capital, Abuja, isn't a default city, like Rabat for Morocco and Port Moresby for Papua New Guinea.

